com.mousebird.maply

Class TileFetchRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.TileFetchRequest

  • public class TileFetchRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic Tile fetcher request. A single request for a single tile of data from a single source. The tile fetcher will... fetch this and call the success or failure callback.

      • fetchInfo

        public java.lang.Object fetchInfo
        This is requested from a TileInfo object by a loader and then passed along to the TileFetcher. TileFetchers expect certain objects. The RemoteTileFetcher wants a RemoteFetchInfo object and will check. Other fetchers will want other things.
